tarts as a straight line and smoothly curves into an upward smile over 3 seconds. The eyebrows also lift slightly to enhance the expression change. The animation loops? No, it's set to fill=\"freeze\" so it stops at the smile state. If you want it to loop, change to fill=\"remove\" and add repeatCount=\"indefinite\". For a single transition as requested, the current code does exactly a 3‑second transition from neutral to smile."}
